query:
SELECT
                ply_upds.tick,
                ply_upds.tiles_owned,
                ply_upds.gold,
                ply_upds.workers,
                ply_upds.troops,
                ply_upds.small_id as "small_id: i16"
            FROM
                analysis_1.packed_player_updates ply_upds
            WHERE
                ply_upds.game_id = $1
                AND ply_upds.tick >= $2
                AND ply_upds.tick < $3
